rows.label: fev11_240_150_msg0001
rows.name:
I believe that concludes my mission.
Shall we head to the flagship?

rows.label: fev11_240_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Fine by me. It's a good place for us
to exchange information.

rows.label: fev11_240_150_msg0003
rows.name:
It's currently moored at
Lascham Cove.

rows.label: fev11_240_150_msg0004
rows.name: Then to Lascham Cove we go!
